'''Violet''' is an [[Italy|Italian]] [[fairy tale]] by [[Giambattista Basile]]. It appears in the ''[[Pentamerone]]'' (''The Tales of tales''), first published in the 1630s.<ref>{{cite book |url=https://www.gutenberg.org/files/2198/2198-h/2198-h.htm#chap12 |title=Project Gutenberg's Stories from Pentamerone, by Giambattista Basile: XII Violet |date=March 1, 2009 |accessdate=May 13, 2017}}</ref>

